title: Ep - 26 - Southern Charm's Craig Conover
description:
Craig Conover from Southern Charm gives scoop on the upcoming season, Erica Rose gives insight on being a contestant on The Bachelor, Kate's sister Megan watches her first episode of Vanderpump Rules, and Sam Chasse and Kate review So Cosmo on the E! network.
